OL,4,Cplaques stolen from churchyard gates
OL,6,FThey were believed to be made of lead
OL,7,For bronze and were put up at the
OL,8,Fchurchyard in 1920.
OL,10,FThe church's reverend has said she is
OL,11,Fheartbroken and she 'doesn't
OL,12,Funderstand how something so callous'
OL,13,Fcould happen.
OL,15,FReverend Andrea Leonard said, "Chatham
OL,16,Fis a military area, so the feeling is
OL,17,Fvery strong.
