OL,4,Cplaques stolen from churchyard gates
OL,6,FPolice say they were stolen between
OL,7,F10pm on Friday 23 May and 10pm on
OL,8,FSaturday 24 May 2025 and are appealing
OL,9,Ffor information.
OL,11,FInvestigating officer, PC Alanya
OL,12,FSpiller, said: "These memorials to
OL,13,Fthose who gave their lives during the
OL,14,FFirst World War have been in place at
OL,15,Fthe church lychgate for over a hundred
OL,16,Fyears.
