OL,3,CReverend left devastated after WW1
OL,4,Cplaques stolen from churchyard gates
OL,6,F"Their loss has had a considerable
OL,7,Fimpact on the local community, and we
OL,8,Fare appealing to anyone who may be
OL,9,Fable to assist our enquiries to
OL,10,Fcontact us."
OL,12,FResidents with private CCTV and
OL,13,Fmotorists with dashcam are also asked
OL,14,Fto check for relevant footage.
OL,16,FThe church say the plaques will be
OL,17,Freplaced as a mark of respect but that
OL,18,Fmaking exact replicas will be hard to
OL,19,Fachieve because they were old.
